Author: pokeswann
Text: Terrible digestion for a while (it gets better, you just have to wait it out), personally I got some headaches, reflux and fatigue. Don’t be discouraged however, this only lasts for the beginning of recovery and you’ll find the positives come soon :)

Author: GirlWearingMyDress
Text: Those are common with anxiety and I know I was super anxious and panicked when I stopped purging.
